_sText:
This map took me many hours to make, it is a bit like Mg_bob.
The aim of the map it to get to the end of this 'obstacle course' like map.

The map has 30 levels progressing in dificulty as you go through them and also has a secret admin room with many weapon spawners.

Please comment on what you realy think of this map and say why..
so if you thinks its not so good tell me why so i can improve on what you have said and produce a better Mg_fred2.

ENJOY...!

****EDIT****

I have made mg_fred_v2 and in which i have fixed lvl 6 so you dont die as much. i have also added 35 spawn points and added lighting
